Package: tbo
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Comic editor built with GTK4
 TBO is a comic and illustrated presentation editor.
 It provides page-based editing, frame-based layout, doodles, bubbles,
 text tools and export options in a GTK4 desktop application.
